346
00:15:04,759 --> 00:15:05,679
person.

347
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:07,519
If you don't mind,

348
00:15:07,799 --> 00:15:08,840
let me take the pictures for you.

349
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:09,440
Okay.

350
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,919
Sorry about that. I have rhinitis.

