352
00:15:32,120 --> 00:15:32,639
Mr. Li,

353
00:15:32,919 --> 00:15:34,240
I've investigated the background
of Yunxiao Fishery's owner.

354
00:15:34,559 --> 00:15:35,639
His name is Tang Zheng.

355
00:15:36,039 --> 00:15:37,279
