379
00:16:22,960 --> 00:16:23,519
Mr. Xie.

380
00:16:24,279 --> 00:16:25,120
Hello.

381
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:25,600
This is

382
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,879
