to hide it any longer.

439
00:18:36,079 --> 00:18:36,599
Actually,

440
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:37,759
I've asked Su Xie Yi about it before.

441
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,319
She admitted

442
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:41,200
