difficult for me?

462
00:19:16,920 --> 00:19:18,400
We're friends indeed.

463
00:19:20,799 --> 00:19:22,160
But I hope we can become

464
00:19:22,279 --> 00:19:23,240
close friends.

465
00:19:23,799 --> 00:19:24,799
