494
00:21:06,359 --> 00:21:07,640
In Fujian, they have
Buddha's temptation.

495
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:09,279
In Jiangzhe, they have
bamboo shoot and salted pork soup.

496
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:10,519
In this world,

497
00:21:10,720 --> 00:21:11,759
